    public invalidate(number: number, multiplier: number) source

    Invalidates whole round with specific number and multiplier.

    Params:

    NameTypeAttributeDescription
    number number

    Number between 0 and 20 plus 25 (bull)
    multiplier number
    • optional
    • default: 1

    Multiplier is between 1 and 3 for all of the numbers but 25 (which has only x2 multiplier).
